{
  "texts": [
    "Combining Propositions 1 and (32), we obtain Result 1.",
    "A possible extension of the model M k with the finite number of payoffs is the extension to the countable number of payoffs in the interval [0, 1].",
    "Such model is formally described as follows.",
    "Let D in [0, 1] be the discrete set of all possible values of X ij.",
    "Each of these values can be obtained with positive probability."
  ]
}